name: Crowned Popper
description: A mixed media art piece, mixing various methods and concepts from freedom of use act to abstract expressionism and digital enhancement. This piece reflects my lifes story as a Puerto Rican American who is passionate about art and struggles as a Combat Veteran. I dedicate this NFT piece to my friend, spiritual brother and art collector Brewse /Twitter:@mitchmurrayag, who’s inspired me to involve myself into NFT
